    "description": "<p><p class=\"Body-Foundation\">Make a <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"spellcast-roll\" nexus=\"daggerheart\"><strong>Spellcast Roll</strong></tooltip> against a target within <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"close\" nexus=\"daggerheart\">Close</tooltip> range. On a success, roll a number of <strong>d20</strong>s equal to your Spellcast trait. The target must make a <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"reaction-roll\" nexus=\"daggerheart\">reaction roll</tooltip> with a <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"difficulty\" nexus=\"daggerheart\">Difficulty</tooltip> equal to your highest result. On a success, the target must mark a <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"stress\" nexus=\"daggerheart\">Stress</tooltip> but isn’t banished. Once per rest on a failure, they are banished from this realm. </p><p class=\"Body-Foundation\">When the PCs roll with <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"fear\" nexus=\"daggerheart\">Fear</tooltip>, the Difficulty gains a −1 penalty and the target makes another reaction roll. On a success, they return from banishment.</p></p>",
